{
  "stem": "8784.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I somehow build it up in my mind that this is in alphabetical order, and therefore, my name, starting with a U, will be at the tail end.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I was extremely anxious throughout the night.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "As it happens, they called me, but not as a very end where the U's would be.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But they did call me someplace.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But the shocking thing is that at that time, when I was so anxious and did not-- did not know fully what was going on, I did not even realize that they called another-- another Urbach by the same name.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And this is not 100% verified, but nevertheless, it appears that way.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They-- they did call another Urbach by the name of David, and David Urbach would have been-- could have been-- my father.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But my anxiety and my fear of that night did not permit me to hear that they called another name by that-- another Urbach.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So I knew nothing of another Urbach winding up in our group at all.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I never met this fellow, David Urbach, at all.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I have no idea.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "See-- well, he appears now on Schindler's list.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so there are only two possibilities how-- how people arrived there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One would have been by way of Gross Rosen, which would have made it likely that maybe my father survived, that maybe it was a different David Urbach.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We will never know that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But this was the-- one of the two possibilities is that somebody came by way of Krakau- Plaszow to Gross Rosen.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
